title: We Are Not Dating『Yet』!! - Novel Updates
genre: Comedy   Romance   School Life   Slice of Life
tags: Calm Protagonist   Childhood Friends   Clever Protagonist   Cohabitation   Glasses-wearing Protagonist   Heartwarming   Male Protagonist   Mature Protagonist   Modern Day

description:
Between Oohata Kazunari and Nakamatsu Yae is a secret that they can’t tell others. That is the fact that they’re『cohabiting』.

However, on the first day of school as third-year high school students, their secret ended up exposed to their classmates because of a tiny incident. From there, the pair’s relationship started to change……

This is a story about a pair who aren’t dating『yet』until they date.>
